1 0 0 1 50 627 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 612 Tm (A production-minded Hybrid RAG system has multiple stages:) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 597 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 582 Tm (1. ingestion) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 567 Tm (2. retrieval) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 552 Tm (3. fusion) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 537 Tm (4. reranking) Tj
