1 0 0 1 50 417 Tm (and testable.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 402 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 387 Tm (2. CORE PRINCIPLES) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 372 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 357 Tm (The repository follows a few important engineering rules:) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 342 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 327 Tm (- use structured data objects instead of loose dictionaries) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 312 Tm (- keep responsibilities separate by module) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 297 Tm (- make every stage independently testable) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 282 Tm (- keep retrieval and generation decoupled) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 267 Tm (- add evaluation only after the corresponding runtime layer exists) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 252 Tm () Tj
