1 0 0 1 50 147 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 132 Tm (1. load raw `.txt` files into `Document`) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 117 Tm (2. split `Document` objects into `Chunk`) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 102 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 87 Tm (This lives under:) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 72 Tm () Tj
